      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been really well-loved? This car has been my pride and joy, and it's still in wonderful shape and ready for plenty more adventures. It runs like a total dream and has been super dependable for me. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to shoot me a message if you have any questions\u2014I'm super easy to talk to and happy to help!",
